@TahaTesser the reason it happens to you with `name` or `givenName` is because you still use `TextInputType.phone`.
If you instead use `TextInputType.name` (basically any non-number keyboard) it will be fine.
So it's a combination of a number keyboard and any autofill hint that causes this issue
